        "body" : "github tarballs do not have the right information for setuptools_scm to compute the version information. The eventual plan is to build this from the pypi sdist, which should work fine and won't need that part of the patch. \r\n\r\nI am patching the `cmake` commands in the `setup.py` so that I can use the custom `cmake` build in the `build.sh`. This lets me force the library to use `OpenMP` on OSX (which is not enabled by default) and makes debugging build issues easier.",
